name: Smol Yellow Window Shutter
description: Smol version of my photograph taken in Paxos isl. this year (2021). In Paxos most window shutters are colored, others green others red and so on.Its traditional way of local architecture and house design to have colored shutters. Some ppl decorate them with objects. This one has a series of seashels. 16x16px George Angelis 2021.
